    "result": {"data":{"markdownRemark":{"excerpt":"Hi Friends üëã, Welcome To aGuideHub!  To create an alert box in React js, you can use the alert function. When you call the alert function. It will show an‚Ä¶","html":"<p>Hi Friends üëã,</p>\n<p>Welcome To aGuideHub! </p>\n<p>To create an alert box in React js, you can use the alert function. When you call the alert function. It will show an alert box on the web page.</p>\n<p>Today, I am going to show you, how to create alert box in react js.</p>\n<p>Table of contents</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Create a show alert function..</li>\n<li>Create the Alert Box.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Let‚Äôs start with the first step.</p>\n<h3>Step 1: Create a show alert function.</h3>\n<p>In the show alert function, I will call the alert method simple messages.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">MyComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">showAlert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'This is an alert message!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>Step 2: Call show alert function.</h3>\n<p>Once you have created the component the alert function. You have to call the show <code class=\"language-text\">alert</code> function <code class=\"language-text\">onclick</code> of a button. You can attach this using the button <code class=\"language-text\">onclick</code> event.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>showAlert<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Click me to show alert<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>ReactJS create alert box example.</h3>\n<p>The below code is an example of The component presents a button with an <code class=\"language-text\">onclick</code> event that triggers a <code class=\"language-text\">showalert</code> function, which displays an <code class=\"language-text\">alert message</code> when the button is clicked.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">App.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'react'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">MyComponent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">showAlert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'This is an alert message!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n      <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button onClick<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>showAlert<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>Click me to show alert<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n    <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>div<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d30259854b2ded0a3f17764d2cbfb334/66be3/alert-box.webp\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 14.556962025316455%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/webp;base64,UklGRkwAAABXRUJQVlA4IEAAAABwAwCdASoUAAMAPtFWpEwoJKOiMAgBABoJZwAAW+u1sD1FioAA/vAbrkFqgOPwyteSkgdpN/qM/NtlE4fPuAAA'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"React, alert box\"\n        title=\"React, alert box\"\n        src=\"/static/d30259854b2ded0a3f17764d2cbfb334/8aab1/alert-box.webp\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d30259854b2ded0a3f17764d2cbfb334/81b7c/alert-box.webp 158w,\n/static/d30259854b2ded0a3f17764d2cbfb334/6ea66/alert-box.webp 315w,\n/static/d30259854b2ded0a3f17764d2cbfb334/8aab1/alert-box.webp 630w,\n/static/d30259854b2ded0a3f17764d2cbfb334/a70f5/alert-box.webp 945w,\n/static/d30259854b2ded0a3f17764d2cbfb334/4ef06/alert-box.webp 1260w,\n/static/d30259854b2ded0a3f17764d2cbfb334/66be3/alert-box.webp 1362w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Here, we are provided code sandbox links for the above program create alert box in React js. Then you can use whenever you went and do the changes as per your requirements.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://aguidehub.com/codesandbox/?code=laughing-antonelli-9k6b0w\" rel=\"nofollow\"  target=\"_BLANK\" >Try it Yourself</a></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to create alert box in react js?","tags":["React"],"date":"March 20, 2023","description":"Example of create alert box in React js with step by step tutorial - aGuideHub","social_image":"media/template/reactjs.jpg"}},"prev":{"frontmatter":{"title":"how to create accordion in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2023-03-21-how-to-create-accordion-in-react-js/"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"How to make mui table with body scrollable in react js?"},"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2023-03-17-how-to-make-mui-table-with-body-scrollable-in-react-js/"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2023-03-20-how-to-create-alert-box-in-react-js/","prevSlug":"/blog/2023-03-21-how-to-create-accordion-in-react-js/","nextSlug":"/blog/2023-03-17-how-to-make-mui-table-with-body-scrollable-in-react-js/"}},
